<div class="post-header post-40615 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-500px-blog category-featured category-homefeed tag-branding-photography tag-creative-photography tag-creative-photoshoot tag-editorial-photography tag-freelance-photography tag-lifestyle-photography tag-lifestyle-photoshoot-tips tag-luxury-aesthetic tag-luxury-lifestyle tag-photography-tips tag-refined-editorial" data-post-id="40615" >
    <article>
        <header class="entry-header">
            <div class="featimg">
                
                    <a href="https://iso.500px.com/achieve-the-luxury-aesthetic-for-editorials/">
                    <!-- <img src="https://iso.500px.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Diana-By-Mateusz-Stefanowski-2.jpeg" alt="The luxury aesthetic and how to achieve it for editorial and lifestyle shoots" > -->
                    <img class="placeholder" src="https://iso.500px.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Diana-By-Mateusz-Stefanowski-2.jpeg" alt="The luxury aesthetic and how to achieve it for editorial and lifestyle shoots" >
                    <div class="background-image" style="background: url(https://iso.500px.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Diana-By-Mateusz-Stefanowski-2.jpeg) no-repeat center center">

                </a>
                
                <div class="feat-overlay">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="columns twelve">
                            <h5 class="category-heading">
                                                                        <a href="https://iso.500px.com/category/500px-blog/" class="">500px Blog</a>                                                                 </h5>
                            <h1 class="entry-title">
                                <a href="https://iso.500px.com/achieve-the-luxury-aesthetic-for-editorials/" title="Permalink to The luxury aesthetic and how to achieve it for editorial and lifestyle shoots" rel="bookmark">
                                                                        The luxury aesthetic and how to achieve it for editorial and lifestyle shoots                                </a>
                            </h1>

                            <p class="entry-meta">
                                Published by 
                                <span class="entry-author">
                                    <a href="https://iso.500px.com/author/featureshoot/" title="Posts by Feature Shoot" rel="author">Feature Shoot</a>                                </span>
                                &bull; 4 years ago                             </p>

                            <div class="entry-share">
                                <ul class="ul-sharing">
                                    <li>
                                        <a class="icon-facebook" target="_blank" href="http://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https://iso.500px.com/achieve-the-luxury-aesthetic-for-editorials/"></a>
                                    </li>
                                    <li>
                                        <a class="icon-twitter" target="_blank" href="http://twitter.com/home?status=The+luxury+aesthetic+and+how+to+achieve+it+for+editorial+and+lifestyle+shoots+https://iso.500px.com/achieve-the-luxury-aesthetic-for-editorials/"></a>
                                    </li>
                                    <li>
                                        <a class="icon-pinterest" target="_blank" href="http://pinterest.com/pin/create/button/?url=https://iso.500px.com/achieve-the-luxury-aesthetic-for-editorials/&amp;media=https://iso.500px.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Diana-By-Mateusz-Stefanowski-2.jpeg&amp;description=The+luxury+aesthetic+and+how+to+achieve+it+for+editorial+and+lifestyle+shoots" ></a>
                                    </li>
